text: Matamata () is a town in the Waikato, New Zealand and located on State Highway 27. It is part of the Matamata-Piako District and is near the Kaimai Ranges. It is the home of Hobbit Movie Set in the Peter Jackson movie set of Lord of the Rings. ==References== Category:Towns in Waikato Category:Matamata-Piako District
title: Matamata
